{"tid":1379982,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一枝強光電筒 光。復香港","createTime":"2019-07-29T01:54:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T06:32:01.000Z","uid":164402,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"233b51f378f146a47789d02f16ecf4a52c2dc69d","tid":1379982,"uid":164402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:54:54.000Z","msg":"雖然連登已經有好多Post講用強光電筒，原理同laser一樣，但laser要瞄到好準，範圍細。但呢個post係教大家實際點買同用<br />\n[［7.21必需］帶電筒，帶電筒，一定要帶電筒！！！]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1329559/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1329559/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YXsQQse.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYXsQQse.jpg&h=627d8940&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GYWKap0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGYWKap0.jpg&h=091406be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n宜家啲狗成日都瞄頭射。其實只要佢射偏少少，或者完全瞄唔到，前線手足會安全好多。<span style=\"color: red;\">去到近戰會更加好用</span><br />\n外國好多police/mility都用當強光電筒做tactical flashlight，平民都會買黎做self defense，咁做係完全合法。<br />\n市面上幾乎所有強光電筒LED都係用一間叫CREE既美國公司生產，所以睇粒LED咩型號就知有幾光，同埋唔會買錯。最經濟個兩粒係XHP50同XHP70。可以出到分別2500同4000lumens。用呢兩粒Chip既電筒aliexpress賣緊~80hkd，淘寶賣貴兩三倍。如果想再平就買XMLT6/L2，1000lumens，大約50hkd。如果想快其實鴨記都有好多鋪賣電筒，價錢可能較貴。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記得買有zoom(變焦)功能</span></span><br />\n下圖:左T6,右XHP70<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RgOXvpi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRgOXvpi.jpg&h=a481fe94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[LED光度比較]<br />\n<a href=\"https://blog.xuite.net/ayubenz/blog/413737120-LED%E7%87%88%E7%9A%84%E9%80%B2%E5%8C%96%28Armytek+Wizard+XHP50%29\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.xuite.net%2Fayubenz%2Fblog%2F413737120-LED%25E7%2587%2588%25E7%259A%2584%25E9%2580%25B2%25E5%258C%2596%2528Armytek%2BWizard%2BXHP50%2529&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4ZyywwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=048a53b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.xuite.net/ayubenz/blog/413737120-LED%E7%87%88%E7%9A%84%E9%80%B2%E5%8C%96%28Armytek+Wizard+XHP50%29</a><br />\n一人一電筒 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光</span></span>復香港"},{"pid":"69f64d7eecd9bfc35a13673bf0bc0d5c2c0e7d4b","tid":1379982,"uid":281720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:56:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f196b00f47a4ca80b978a1ac7fbeccd746b3e8e2","tid":1379982,"uid":164402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:17:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d7c7edd087394dffc3010115389e334405620927","tid":1379982,"uid":11849,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:53:20.000Z","msg":"第一幅圖射對面樓好痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n粒電用到幾耐?"},{"pid":"0a0d2ab7968a917b2f487a0e470e7f14c8698a20","tid":1379982,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:54:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日(7月29)1500-1830</span></span>會有義工係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">旺角東天橋</span></span>擺街站等無上連登的市民都可以寫底感受比我地,希望大家支持<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"e21d4e86d11ffa4d57b652b1ea037606cc2efd2e","tid":1379982,"uid":11849,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:54:54.000Z","msg":"撤退果陣射住速龍係咪有用?"},{"pid":"c0cacf35f2ad71a4e63d56c7e7e275387c921671","tid":1379982,"uid":164402,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d7c7edd087394dffc3010115389e334405620927","tid":1379982,"uid":11849,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-